{"tid":1420652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手帶風向，以後一定要分區，開多重戰線","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:50.000Z","uid":57044,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"231802ce13e080cc6935682549ac83f152148981","tid":1420652,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"見到連登好多po帶錯誤風向叫人唔好開多戰線，話會少記者等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊記，我地最怕係<br />\n1. 圍捕<br />\n2. 煙加速龍突襲<br />\n<br />\n以上兩樣都係要大隊警察先做到，圍捕起碼要 5 到6隊防暴先做到。我地琴日搞7區，警察明顯無力圍捕，最多可以單面推進！ <br />\n<br />\n另外！ 一個大優勢係，狗琴日唔夠人再封鎖區域，set roadblock同埋安排人搜地鐵。所以，7區光復係絕對絕對正確戰略決定，加上有大量街坊加成，我地係穩操勝卷。所以，幫手推，帶風向</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1131e5017b98a823da28c64e51fa5e6c948c8d52","tid":1420652,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83a551987df67f700da8dc302e618c24e65a82cc","tid":1420652,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fd9c273a97d1ea34e9d1c9234e0d501a6de8312","tid":1420652,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29777ec366603b9defffe226d4c74baece9e35f3","tid":1420652,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"幫手推，好人一生平安"}]}